lock/\">&#8220;Latest Posts&#8221; block</a> in WordPress.org; it&#8217;s just a list of posts. The difference is the way the posts are displayed:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul data-carousel-extra=\'{\"blog_id\":45531309,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/themeshaper.com\\/2019\\/01\\/29\\/a-schema-for-gutenberg-blocks\\/\"}\' class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"7136\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/latest_posts_block/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/latest_posts_block.png\" data-orig-size=\"634,222\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"latest_posts_block\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/latest_posts_block.png?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/latest_posts_block.png?w=634\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/latest_posts_block.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7136\" data-link=\"https://themeshaper.com/latest_posts_block/\" class=\"wp-image-7136\" /><figcaption>Latest Posts</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"7135\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13-07-34/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png\" data-orig-size=\"1346,608\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=840\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=840\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7135\" data-link=\"https://themeshaper.com/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13-07-34/\" class=\"wp-image-7135\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=840 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=150 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=300 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=768 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png?w=1024 1024w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.07.34.png 1346w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption>Related Posts</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>There are <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/1594\">plans afoot</a> to update the &#8220;Latest Posts&#8221; block, so that it contains an image and a post summary (see image below).</p>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra=\'{\"blog_id\":45531309,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/themeshaper.com\\/2019\\/01\\/29\\/a-schema-for-gutenberg-blocks\\/\"}\' class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\">\n<div data-carousel-extra=\'{\"blog_id\":45531309,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/themeshaper.com\\/2019\\/01\\/29\\/a-schema-for-gutenberg-blocks\\/\"}\' class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p>As these two blocks grow they seem to be converging on similar layouts, but with different content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are similar overlaps with other blocks. For example the layout of the WordPress.org <a href=\"https://en.support.wordpress.com/wordpress-editor/blocks/gallery-block/\">gallery block</a> could also be used to display a list of posts, as could the recently launched <a href=\"https://jetpack.com/support/jetpack-blocks/tiled-gallery-block/\">Tiled Gallery block</a>. Evidently there are many layout possibilities for a list of posts!</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra=\'{\"blog_id\":45531309,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/themeshaper.com\\/2019\\/01\\/29\\/a-schema-for-gutenberg-blocks\\/\"}\' class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img data-attachment-id=\"7137\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13-18-43/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.18.43.png\" data-orig-size=\"1250,1496\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.18.43\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.18.43.png?w=251\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.18.43.png?w=840\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-29-at-13.18.43.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7137\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h4>The problem</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>As the number of Gutenberg blocks grows these overlaps become more obvious. As we start to build pages with Gutenberg it starts to become apparent that this is going to get very messy very quickly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Essentially blocks have a content and a presentation element.  Taking the example we began with, we can see overlap between many different types of content:</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Lists of content</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>One type of content is a list of text, images and links. These come in many different forms, but they share the same structure:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Latest posts</li><li>List of posts in a category</li><li>List of post in a tag</li><li>Archive of posts by month/year etc</li><li>List of categories/tags</li><li>List featured posts</li><li>List of images</li><li>List of authors</li><li>List of [custom post type]</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Similarly, all of the above types of content could be displayed in any of the following ways:</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Layouts</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some examples of the different types of layout that this content could use:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul data-carousel-extra=\'{\"blog_id\":45531309,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/themeshaper.com\\/2019\\/01\\/29\\/a-schema-for-gutenberg-blocks\\/\"}\' class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"7138\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/screenshot-2019-01-28-at-17-10-06/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/screenshot-2019-01-28-at-17.10.06.png\" data-orig-size=\"532,578\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;