s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"enclosure\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:67:\"https://videos.files.wordpress.com/P8q7dcHc/music-theme-demo_hd.mp4\";s:6:\"length\";s:8:\"25077760\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"video/mp4\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Kjell Reigstad\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16625:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">A couple months ago, I created</span><a href=\"https://github.com/Automattic/gutenberg-themes-sketch\"> <span style=\"font-weight:400;\">a Sketch document</span></a><span style=\"font-weight:400;\"> to assist with the design of block-driven themes. I posted about that</span><a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/\"> <span style=\"font-weight:400;\">here on Themeshaper</span></a><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">, and provided a couple short examples of how it could be used in a theme design workflow. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Since then, Allan Cole and I have been working to make one of those examples — a site for an imagined band named Superserious — into a working example of a Gutenberg-powered WordPress theme. We named the theme “<em>Music</em>.”</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Allan and I set out to experiment, learn, and create a resource for the community. We’ve documented our experience designing and building this theme, and will be publishing our notes in a series of posts here on Themeshaper. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">To kick things off, we’re </span><a href=\"https://github.com/automattic/musictheme\"><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">releasing <em>Music</em> on GitHub</span></a><span style=\"font-weight:400;\"> today. We’d love for you to give it a spin, tinker with it, and explore how it works with Gutenberg. Here are a few things to look out for: </span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Design</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Our design goal for the theme has been to show that it’s possible (and encouraged!) to make a Gutenberg theme that doesn’t necessarily look like Gutenberg. We wanted to create something bold and a little experimental; a theme with somewhat aggressive, non-standard styles. </span></p>\n<p>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/01-homepage-mobile/\'><img width=\"84\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-mobile.png?w=84\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-mobile.png?w=84 84w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-mobile.png?w=168 168w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 84px) 85vw, 84px\" data-attachment-id=\"7050\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/01-homepage-mobile/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-mobile.png\" data-orig-size=\"750,1334\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-homepage-mobile\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-mobile.png?w=169\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-mobile.png?w=576\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/02-tour-desktop/\'><img width=\"98\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-tour-desktop.jpg?w=98\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-tour-desktop.jpg?w=98 98w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-tour-desktop.jpg?w=196 196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 98px) 85vw, 98px\" data-attachment-id=\"7052\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/02-tour-desktop/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-tour-desktop.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1960,3000\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-tour-desktop\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-tour-desktop.jpg?w=196\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-tour-desktop.jpg?w=669\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/03-archive-desktop/\'><img width=\"98\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/03-archive-desktop.jpg?w=98\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/03-archive-desktop.jpg?w=98 98w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/03-archive-desktop.jpg?w=196 196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 98px) 85vw, 98px\" data-attachment-id=\"7054\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/03-archive-desktop/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/03-archive-desktop.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1960,3000\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-archive-desktop\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/03-archive-desktop.jpg?w=196\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/03-archive-desktop.jpg?w=669\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/02-homepage-mobile2/\'><img width=\"84\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-homepage-mobile2.png?w=84\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-homepage-mobile2.png?w=84 84w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-homepage-mobile2.png?w=168 168w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 84px) 85vw, 84px\" data-attachment-id=\"7051\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/02-homepage-mobile2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-homepage-mobile2.png\" data-orig-size=\"750,1334\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-homepage-mobile2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-homepage-mobile2.png?w=169\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/02-homepage-mobile2.png?w=576\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/01-homepage-desktop/\'><img width=\"98\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-desktop.jpg?w=98\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-desktop.jpg?w=98 98w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-desktop.jpg?w=196 196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 98px) 85vw, 98px\" data-attachment-id=\"7049\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/01-homepage-desktop/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-desktop.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1960,3000\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-homepage-desktop\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-desktop.jpg?w=196\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/01-homepage-desktop.jpg?w=669\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8/\'><img width=\"84\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8.png?w=84\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8.png?w=84 84w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8.png?w=168 168w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 84px) 85vw, 84px\" data-attachment-id=\"7069\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8.png\" data-orig-size=\"750,1334\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"musictheme.mystagingwebsite.com_tour_(iPhone 6_7_8)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8.png?w=169\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/musictheme-mystagingwebsite-com_tour_iphone-6_7_8.png?w=576\" /></a>\n</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Gutenberg gives users unprecedented control over their site design, opening the door for variety and experimentation. Our favorite example of this is our cover image blocks. They look great out of the gate, but users can adjust the image, alignment, and color to achieve a wide range of looks:</span></p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"7055\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/cover-images/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png\" data-orig-size=\"2268,1008\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"cover-images\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png?w=840\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7055\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png\" alt=\"cover-images.png\" width=\"2268\" height=\"1008\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png 2268w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png?w=150&amp;h=67 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png?w=300&amp;h=133 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png?w=768&amp;h=341 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/cover-images.png?w=1024&amp;h=455 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Development</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">You’ll be happy to hear that the overall theme development process wasn’t all that different with Gutenberg. Common patterns like headers, footers, and loops work just as you’d expect in a Gutenberg-powered theme. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">In many areas, Gutenberg makes things easier for both users and developers. For instance, full-width header images used to require a custom-built customizer or theme option solution, but now they’re essentially built in. This was important to keep in mind while building the theme, and was a very positive change for development.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Creating stylesheets for blocks was pretty straightforward. Expanding on the built-in stylesheets in </span><code>_s</code><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">,  we added a </span><code>blocks.scss</code><span style=\"font-weight:400;\"> file to the SASS directory and placed all of our block-specific styles and overrides there. This kept everything nice and organized and is likely to </span><a href=\"https://github.com/Automattic/_s/issues/1248\"><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">appear in </span><code>_s</code><span style=\"font-weight:400;\"> in the future</span></a><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Since Gutenberg is output by </span><code>the_content()</code><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">, we learned to take special care with any wrapper </span><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">div</span><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">s that might clip or obstruct the expected behavior of Gutenberg blocks. We&#8217;ll talk more about that in a follow up post. </span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight:400;\"><br />\nBlock Styles</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">We’re truly excited about the custom editor styles that ship with <em>Music</em>. These styles are a breakthrough: they give users a much clearer sense of what their visitors will see on the front end.<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"v-P8q7dcHc-1\" class=\"video-player\" style=\"width:840px;height:560px\">\n<embed id=\"v-P8q7dcHc-1-video\" src=\"https://v0.wordpress.com/player.swf?v=1.04&amp;guid=P8q7dcHc&amp;isDynamicSeeking=true\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" title=\"Music Theme Demo\" wmode=\"direct\" seamlesstabbing=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" overstretch=\"true\"></embed></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">Best of all (for theme developers at least), the editor styles were a breeze to integrate! We built all of these in over the course of just a few hours.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\"><br />\nLike most of the work we do, the Music theme is open source. You can find it on GitHub: </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/automattic/musictheme/\"><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">https://github.com/automattic/musictheme/</span></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">If you’d just like to see the front end, feel free to click around our demo site here: </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://musictheme.mystagingwebsite.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">https://musictheme.mystagingwebsite.com/</span></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">In many ways, designing and building this theme was similar to the way we’ve made themes in the past — but we did carve out a few new practices along the way. Allan and I will be sharing them with you in upcoming posts. In the meantime, we encourage you to download, install, and experiment with <em>Music</em> yourself!</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Read part two of this series: <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/06/04/designing-a-gutenberg-powered-theme-music/\">Designing a Gutenberg-Powered Theme: Music</a></em></p>\n<div><a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/\"><img alt=\"Music Theme Demo\" src=\"https://videos.files.wordpress.com/P8q7dcHc/music-theme-demo_std.original.jpg\" width=\"160\" height=\"120\" /></a></div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/05/22/music-a-gutenberg-powered-theme/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\